{"tid":1591661,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警不是香港人","createTime":"2019-09-24T08:58:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T13:35:40.000Z","uid":36797,"like":47,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"e363e0bb877188af11d713f0000cc3a58b3a858c","tid":1591661,"uid":36797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T08:58:20.000Z","msg":"講左咁耐麻布袋無人出手；前線用火魔法但永遠唔掉黑警；幾個圍住隻狗黎打但係隻狗都無穿無爛，點解？？<br />\n<br />\n我地要承認一樣野，香港人好斯文，唔夠膽，唔敢放手一駁，而且由細到大接受既教育，令到我地道德枷鎖好重。<br />\n聖人不死，大盜不止。咁我地要點樣擺脫依個枷鎖？不如學下黑警。<br />\n佢地可以做到咁狠，係因為佢地排左軍隊以外既人都唔係人，係喬裝既示威者，係敵人，係Object，係甲由。<br />\n<br />\n睇番我地陣容，一直以黎都好自豪自己係香港人身份，加上前排所謂「國歌」一出，不少人都為之感動，點解？因為係個身份認同，以往香港人成日話「你去到外國，人地咪淨係當你chinese」，但而家開始有改變了，「香港」兩隻字慢慢脫離「中國」，我講緊係國際層面，而唔係自己圍內共識。<br />\n<br />\n番去主題：黑警不是香港人。<br />\n如果大家想廣大市民、香港人接受到我地還手；<br />\n如果大家想前線用魔法更加狠；<br />\n如果大家想每次發夢見到防暴唔係走，而係向住佢地衝。<br />\n如果大家想幫更多人衝破心理關口，我地就要大規模宣揚：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警不是香港人</span></span>"},{"pid":"e8d83ce6f7a66092f7327b85c9718d2e2ac1b631","tid":1591661,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T08:59:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">國&hearts;際&hearts;戰&hearts;線&hearts;需&hearts;要&hearts;你</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RH29z9Z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRH29z9Z.jpg&h=787fa8fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f229cfdb703b2c8c94838adaadd8c23c9ceb2969","tid":1591661,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:00:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YRFK8KD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYRFK8KD.jpg&h=15361d85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mBcEXDa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmBcEXDa.jpg&h=7e67508d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">924放映會 927 新屋嶺 928民陣集會 929 全球抗共 10.1國殤遊行</code></pre>"},{"pid":"6a52516b0977ac2faf44d296185d6c31b1d40555","tid":1591661,"uid":72602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:01:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/U0bROga.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FU0bROga.jpg&h=5e267a10&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b7a9add9707afdb6218c882a4ac23f364d4445fb","tid":1591661,"uid":36797,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:02:01.000Z","msg":"大家跟我講一次<br />\n<br />\n黑警不是香港人"},{"pid":"56790d553f91b36aa8f35d78f8ce0ee1722b5471","tid":1591661,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:03:08.000Z","msg":"關斯文咩事啫<br />\n個個有飯食有屋住有iphone 用<br />\n點解要冒咁大風險去麻包袋黑警？<br />\n自己唔做就唔好再開呢啲post 影響啲細路仔，十八歲都未夠既學生去做"},{"pid":"5ff7df58033a568134f699d761511170689a8950","tid":1591661,"uid":321672,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:04:41.000Z","msg":"比起外國<br />\n香港算係斯文啦"},{"pid":"4b5543502158dbe3f8766c99de6a5ee2270ac621","tid":1591661,"uid":63300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:17:39.000Z","msg":"冇人做，樓主咪試下做第一個"},{"pid":"70edf03917cb2686f6722df1b59b55bb062a9467","tid":1591661,"uid":36797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b5543502158dbe3f8766c99de6a5ee2270ac621","tid":1591661,"uid":63300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:17:39.000Z","msg":"冇人做，樓主咪試下做第一個"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:21:26.000Z","msg":"如果有睇哂內文，我唔係叫人去做，只係提出一句新口號，提高大家排外意識，就算之後真係有人做咩出黎，社會都更易接受。<br />\n<br />\n對住班黑警次次都黑社會、黑社會，對佢地又無傷害，對我地又無益。"},{"pid":"38a23cdb8c87d113baab2c18645493608e530e13","tid":1591661,"uid":17866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:25:46.000Z","msg":"恐怖分子唔係人<br />\n要血腥清洗，光復世界文明，毒瘤移除"},{"pid":"5516c811fc9f3d04b8d3f447fbe2a8b7ca3ad5ab","tid":1591661,"uid":255637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:28:33.000Z","msg":"思維正確"},{"pid":"f62d86e6ecd5c5e5ff06e676953a41f9d06e412d","tid":1591661,"uid":221360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:32:56.000Z","msg":"大家要記住呀！！！！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">929反赤納粹行動</span></span>，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">全球呀！</span></strong></span><br />\n我地唔可以輸比世界上任何一個地區，我地幾咁憎赤納粹<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">要求正虎黑警交代831，新屋嶺！要求了解被捕義士情況！求真相求解釋！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仲有仲有，唔好唔記得今個月大家有咩要做呀！！！</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DPoppm7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDPoppm7.png&h=0935ebd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nYT48OO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnYT48OO.png&h=cc06dc40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n推推推推推，p牌仔開唔到post唯有洗爆你地留言！"},{"pid":"eba67cf6d5c5598a5ea9865956f17a05a925cdb5","tid":1591661,"uid":62558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:42:43.000Z","msg":"要對準政權 係政府走狗"},{"pid":"cf43d394672e37aea9bf6dcb7c6cfa5ac4a2c593","tid":1591661,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:50:30.000Z","msg":"解散警隊重新招募絕非不可行！分析填補新警力嘅來源！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1591746\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1591746</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0e7e3ebe584333e0f8d2b06a6ec69725d3c370cb","tid":1591661,"uid":36797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf43d394672e37aea9bf6dcb7c6cfa5ac4a2c593","tid":1591661,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,